Name: SYMMETRY alpha
About the game: SYMMETRY is a VR software tool for professionals in architecture, engineering, and construction. SYMMETRY converts CADs into VR with a highly intuitive man-machine interface, enabling users across several industries to communicate ideas and direction with ease to efficiently facilitate consensus formation. Supported file formats: .skp(SketchUp)
